ty density, the larger valley\npolarization can be obtained.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2016 07:15:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Jun 2016 07:46:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-21"}
